NAME
  vtkSHYXDataSetToPartitionedCollection
  DESCRIPTION
  "Split vtkDataSet into vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection: tetrahedra, then node_sets/side_sets from first-component <=0 merged + >=1 connectivity split (vtkThreshold BETWEEN) or feature-angle connectivity."
GROUPS
  Meshing
DEPENDS
  VTK::CommonCore
  VTK::CommonDataModel
  VTK::CommonExecutionModel
  VTK::FiltersCore
  VTK::FiltersExtraction
  VTK::FiltersGeometry
  VTK::IOIOSS
